    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Austrelatus gen. nov., a new genus of Australasian diving beetles (Coleoptera, Dytiscidae, Copelatinae), with the discovery of 31 new species from New Guinea" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figures66-69>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figure71>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figure84>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figures87-88>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figures1-2> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figures66-69>
    dc:description "Figures 66 - 69. Habitus and colouration of 66 Austrelatus rouaffer sp. nov. 67 A. wanggarensis sp. nov. 68 A. vagauensis sp. nov. 69 A. sandaunensis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881150" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figure71>
    dc:description "Figure 71. Austrelatus wanggarensis sp. nov., median lobe A left lateral view B right lateral view C ventral view D left paramere in external view E right paramere in internal view. Scale bar: one unit - 0.1 mm (A-C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881152" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figure84>
    dc:description "Figure 84. Map of New Guinea showing distribution of 14 Austrelatus species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881162" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figures87-88>
    dc:description "Figures 87, 88. Habitats of Austrelatus species 87 small forest pool at track Nabire-Ilaga, Km 62: type localities of A. innominatus sp. nov. and A. pseudooksibilensis sp. nov. and habitats of A. febrisauri sp. nov., A. rugosus sp. nov., and A. kaszabi (Guignot, 1956) 88 partly shaded rest pool of an intermittent stream at the road Wanggar to Bali Bumi: type locality of A. wanggarensis sp. nov. Photographs by LH." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881164" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1170.103834.figures1-2>
    dc:description "Figures 1, 2. Median lobe in left lateral view A and left paramere in external view B of 1 Copelatus portior Guignot, 1956 2 C. martinbaehri Hendrich et al., 2019; a median process." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881108" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

